modelCheckCTL.model
Class KripkeStruct

java.lang.Object
  modelCheckCTL.model.KripkeStruct

public class KripkeStruct
extends java.lang.Object

The parser will take a text file that describes a kripke structure and build a directed graph. It will use the KripkeStruct object to do this.

resetKripkeStruct

public void resetKripkeStruct()
Reset the kripke structure to evaluate another formula. The list of satisfied formulas needs to be cleared and the index needs to be reset so the Strongly Connected Components can be re-calculated.
